---
title: One-Pan Soy-Glazed Steak Banh Mi with Sesame Slaw & Chili Mayo
description: One type of cuisine found in nearly every part of the world? The sandwich! Our take on the Vietnamese banh mi combines textures and sweet and savory flavors between two slices of bread: The split baguette is filled with a sweet soy-glazed steak, fresh cucumber, sesame slaw, cilantro and as much chili mayo as you like. You're *soy* going to love it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-soy-glazed-steak-banh-mi-d29e819f.jpg
